text: Red vine or redvine may refer to: * Basella alba, a vegetable also known as red vine spinach * Brunnichia, a genus of woody vines known as redvine * Red Vines, a brand of licorice * "Red Vines", a song from the Aimee Mann album Bachelor No. 2 or, the Last Remains of the Dodo * Red Vine, a race horse * The Red Vine, a painting by George Bellows * Siphlophis compressus, also known as red vine snake
title: Red vine
